847f","tid":2145040,"uid":363335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T02:32:06.000Z","msg":"Computer Engineering 你入 IEEE student membership，睇下佢有啲咩 member's benefit course 你有興趣學啦，由 MOSFET 到 machine learning 乜 L 都有。入咗 IEEE，畢業後有得投功能組別添啊（假如到時香港仲有立法會選舉）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T04:06:37.000Z","msg":"Electrical engine hd grad 可唔可以入ieee 做正式member？<br />\nmechan degree grad 又得唔得？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T04:17:47.000Z","msg":"Elec 一定得<br />\nMechanical 唔知"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T04:43:51.000Z","msg":"我見佢咁寫<br />\n1.有3-5年嘅university level 或 higher degree（我嘅理解係postgrad），而且係 IEEE designated field，可以直接入會<br />\n<br />\n2.有3-5年嘅university level 或higher degree，但非IEEE designated field，不過有3年喺IEEE designated field嘅工作經驗<br />\n<br />\n3.冇任何學歷，不過有6年喺IEEE designated field嘅工作經驗<br />\n<br />\nThe designated fields are: Engineering, Computer Sciences and Information Technology, Physical Sciences, Biological and Medical Sciences, Mathematics, Technical Communications, Education, Management, and Law and Policy. <br />\n<br />\n香港hd得2年，而且唔算university level，咁點解<br />\n而mechan degree 我見有機會得<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ieee.org/membership/qualifications.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ieee.org%2Fmembership%2Fqualifications.html&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=2e4e61b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ieee.org/membership/qualifications.html</a>"},{"pid":"cefd6280f39daa468a41a43179bc49a7e9f9715a","tid":2145040,"uid":2151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T04:45:50.000Z","msg":"High dip ee <br />\nDegree me<br />\nMaster ce"}]}